Text:
Screw that, EVERYONE knows that it is utter blasphemy to upload a video without screenshots. Click on ANY video file without screens and read the dozens of comments blasting the person for not providing screenshots.

It would be better for everyone if this was never uploaded. Because of shit like this, I have to spent large amounts of time downloading worthless files and searching through file after file in order to find videos with proper quality. If dumb asses like this simply posted the screens, all of us could find the specific quality video we are looking for quickly and without hassle.

So yeah, no thanks; please don't upload videos without screens. It makes this wonderful website that much more crappy.
